DISPLAY CHLAUTH(channel-name)

DISPLAY QMGR CHLAUTH


ALTER QMGR CHLAUTH(ENABLED)



Add Custom Rules (Optional)
For example, to allow a specific user on a SVRCONN channel:


SET CHLAUTH('MY.SVRCONN') TYPE(USERMAP) CLNTUSER('appuser') MCAUSER('mqapp')


5. Refresh Security

REFRESH SECURITY TYPE(CHLAUTH)
